-- models/intermediate/int_users_with_company.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        u.user_id,
        u.company_id,
        c.industry

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_subscriptions_with_plan.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        s.subscription_id,
        s.user_id,
        s.plan_id,
        s.started_at,
        s.status,
        p.tier,
        p.monthly_price
    FROM {{ ref('stg_subscriptions') }} s
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_plans') }} p
        ON p.plan_id = s.plan_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_billing.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        subscription_id,
        event_month,
        amount,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY subscription_id, event_month
            ORDER BY event_id DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_billing_events') }}
)
SELECT
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

```sql
-- models/facts/fct_subscription_metrics.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        b.event_month AS month,
        COALESCE(sp.tier, '(unknown)') AS tier,
        COALESCE(uc.industry, '(unknown)') AS industry,
        COUNT(DISTINCT sp.subscription_id) AS active_subscriptions,
        SUM(sp.monthly_price) AS total_mrr,
        COUNT(DISTINCT sp.user_id) AS unique_users
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_billing') }} b
    INNER JOIN {{ ref('int_subscriptions_with_plan') }} sp
        ON sp.subscription_id = b.subscription_id
    INNER JOIN {{ ref('int_users_with_company') }} uc
        ON uc.user_id = sp.user_id
    GROUP BY
        b.event_month,
        sp.tier,
        uc.industry
)
SELECT * FROM source
ORDER BY
    month,
    tier,
    industry
